“Donna OG is a 50/50 hybrid and is accurately depicted.

Donna OG is a cross of Mary OG with Larry OG, 
and then backcrossing once again with a ML11 phenotype of the Mary OG. 

Nug structure is flawless, dark cones with a sea of dark colors, an array of trichromes, & a a sweet, piney aroma.
Smoke is full, thick and flavorful, clean and piney, citrus/sweet flavor at the tip.

High feels like a dreamy euphoria over the ...”
